<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4759385>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 6. Hesperoperla pacifica complex monophasic-grouped call patterns based upon individual average interbeat intervals i1-i7 and average inter-group intervals igi1-igi14 (msec) for one Butte Creek (BC) and two Domingo Spring (DS) 2007 analysis groups. A) White bars = BC reared male calls (N=120), B) Gray bars = DS collected male calls (N=69) and C) Black bars = DS reared male calls (N=22). Y-axis ranges from 50-250 msec." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4759385/files/figure.png" .

